efault on your profile"> Only his amazing inner spirit and newly discovered Toujin attack allowed him to force prevail.</span></li></ul></li></ul><ul><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DangerousForbiddenTechnique" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DangerousForbiddenTechnique">Dangerous Forbidden Technique</a>: The Devil King Sword's <em>Full Moon Attack</em> is powerful enough to wipe out a planet and turn the Earth into a Dead Star. That's the reason why the moon is a barren wasteland. <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> Onimaru uses it anyway in order to kill Yaiba.</span>.</li></ul><ul><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DemonicPossession" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DemonicPossession">Demonic Possession</a>: What happens to both Onimaru and Yaiba when they awakened Fujin/Raijin's spirit. In Onimru's case, Fujin "agreed" to merge with Onimaru. <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> Later weaponized against the mind-reading Diamond by summoning both spirits into his body</span>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DevourTheDragon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DevourTheDragon">Devour the Dragon</a>: <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> After getting hit by the Half Moon blast, Kaguya merge with all the Moon Bunnies (included Gekko and Tsukikage) in order to become more powerful. Also the Spiderman got assimilated by Yamata no Orochi's flesh</span>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DiagonalCut" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DiagonalCut">Diagonal Cut</a>: Kaminari Giri, as seen <a class="urllink" href="http://t2.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS-vVjKTYmNZJu6lIcgm_BZf0T5RhXxe9dIIBVxcCuCj8cnOiCP8w&amp;t=1">here<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a> . Als