neWingedAngel">One-Winged Angel</a> form she can <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BeamSpam" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BeamSpam">Beam Spam</a> the hell out of her enemies via <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EyeBeams" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EyeBeams">Eye Beams</a>.</span></li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EpicFlail" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EpicFlail">Epic Flail</a>: Kotaro's Kusarigama has a huge iron weight. Also Silver's <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WeaponOfChoice" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WeaponOfChoice">Weapon of Choice</a>. And he can pull it out of his mouth</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EveryJapaneseSwordIsAKatana" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EveryJapaneseSwordIsAKatana">Every Japanese Sword Is a Katana</a>: Averted: The Katana of Fujin and Raijin don't look like typical katanas and the Ryujin sword is more a Tsurugi (straight sword).</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EverythingsBetterWithMonkeys" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EverythingsBetterWithMonkeys">Everything's Better with Monkeys</a>: Averted with Basho Matsuo, who transform into a Chimpanzee and is an utter bastard.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EverythingsBetterWithSpinning" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EverythingsBetterWithSpinning">Everything's Better with Spinning</a>:<ul><li> Yaiba's Senpuken and Kazaguruma attacks, but not the "Yaiba Boomerang"....</li><li> Onimaru's Tornado Attack involves spinning. <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> later Yaiba manages to learn this technique</span>.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EvilWeapon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EvilWeapon">Evil Weapon</a>: The Devil King Sword (Mao Ken), forged by the Moon People, has the power of absorb the evil within a person and 