 (Hao Ken), born by merging together the swords of Raijin and Fujin, and is the good counterpart of the Devil King Sword.</span></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InformedAbility" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InformedAbility">Informed Ability</a>: Played for laughs with the Ant Soldier, who is described as the strongest of all the Soldiers combined... but is Ant-sized too...</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InstantAwesomeJustAddDragons" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InstantAwesomeJustAddDragons">Instant Awesome: Just Add Dragons!</a>: Yaiba's first attempt to use the Gold Orb powers turned him into a small dragon. <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">Also the White Dragon summoned by Ryujin's Sword</span>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InstantFlightJustAddSpinning" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InstantFlightJustAddSpinning">Instant Flight: Just Add Spinning!</a>: During the Legendary Orbs arc, it is revealed that the Starfishman, a former Hakki, can use spinning in order to fly around.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Kappa" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Kappa">Kappa</a>: Kerokichi, the cute Kappa living inside the Darkness Orb. Also Kerosuke, who is a Gargantuan, well muscled and firebreathing Kappa. Our Kappas Are Different.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KiManipulation" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KiManipulation">Ki Manipulation</a>: Many of them from Kaguya Arc onward.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KidSamurai" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KidSamurai">Kid Samurai</a>: Well, Duh...<ul><li> Also Soshi Okita is very young.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KillItWithFire" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KillItWithFire">Kill It with Fire</a>: The fate of Shiro and Goemon. Also Burner's Modus Operandi.</li><li