ants to unseal</span>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OurVampiresAreDifferent" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OurVampiresAreDifferent">Our Vampires Are Different</a>:<ul><li> Bat Guy! A grey <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WingedHumanoid" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WingedHumanoid">Winged Humanoid</a> with sunglasses, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RoyalRapier" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RoyalRapier">Royal Rapier</a> and <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GratuitousEnglish" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GratuitousEnglish">Gratuitous English</a>, and he's also a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ArsonMurderAndJaywalking" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ArsonMurderAndJaywalking">fanboy of Musashi</a>.</li><li> Furthermore when he bites Yaiba he transform into a Werewolf. Even he <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LampshadeHanging" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LampshadeHanging">doesn't know why</a>.</li><li> In the Spanish dub he speaks Spanish with a thick British accent. And <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HilarityEnsues" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HilarityEnsues">he's funny as Hell.</a>.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OverlyLongTongue" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OverlyLongTongue">Overly Long Tongue</a>: Gerozaemon, who often weaponized it. Also Chameleon Bonaparte. This lead to a epic Tongue duel between the two.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheOwlKnowingOne" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheOwlKnowingOne">The Owl-Knowing One</a>: While looking for the Orb in Biwa Lake, Yaiba ask for help to an Old, large Owl. Who want to get paid for his services.<div class="indent"> <strong>Sayaka</strong>:".... not so cute, after all..".</div></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PaperThinDisguise" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PaperThi